{"tid":1526962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【我係民建聯會員，我呼籲大家不要再投民建聯】","createTime":"2019-09-01T08:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:22:22.000Z","uid":117638,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6eba02e2588b821a55ec85be057cddd416649ef3","tid":1526962,"uid":117638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htMV80m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtMV80m.jpg&h=b04b25d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvwSrNp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxvwSrNp.jpg&h=6fab750c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【我是民建聯黨員，我反對警察】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1526588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1526588</a><br />\n<br />\n鑑於我標題起得不好，有人誤會了我是來幫DAB洗底，我另開po，以民建聯會員（但剪咗卡）、淺藍中產的身分重新呼籲：為香港好，為家人好，為民生好，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以後一票不投建制派！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7545f2930d1df0712aaf90e817434fe022292d3e","tid":1526962,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:15:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"691dca2139a8b20a0948de97b80b45bd79c9f2d3","tid":1526962,"uid":144594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33e2fff6bb1e7a93e2d64fdde72c3d2f5629484","tid":1526962,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:16:05.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"75ef23b127743383bf9883d69e3a32c2c7c43515","tid":1526962,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"退左黨未呀？"},{"pid":"5a8e2955e17e76fca674c0